      "order": 13,
      "mode": 0,
      "properties": {"text": "## DWPose + Flux ControlNet Workflow\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Install comfyui_controlnet_aux (ComfyUI Manager)\n2. Install ComfyUI-FluxControlNet (ComfyUI Manager)\n3. Download flux1-dev.safetensors → models/checkpoints/\n4. Download flux-controlnet-pose.safetensors (InstantX/FLUX.1-dev-Controlnet-Pose) → models/controlnet/\n5. DWPose model auto-downloads on first run via comfyui_controlnet_aux\n\n**LoRA:** Replace 'your_character_lora.safetensors' in node 5 with your trained LoRA. Set strength=0.0 to bypass.\n\n**Tuning:** ControlNet strength 0.6-0.85 for pose faithfulness vs creativity tradeoff."}
    },
    {
