      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [560, 1100],
      "size": {"0": 380, "1": 160},
      "flags": {},
      "order": 14,
      "mode": 0,
      "properties": {"text": "## Alternative: SDPose-OOD (March 2026)\n\nFor out-of-distribution poses (extreme angles, partial occlusion, non-standard clothing):\n- Install ComfyUI-SDPose-OOD node\n- Replace DWPreprocessor (node 2) with SDPoseOOD node\n- Same ControlNet downstream — drop-in replacement\n- Better robustness on DAZ/Blender renders vs real photos"}
    }
